Package jade.core.management

Class AgentManagementProxy

java.lang.Object
jade.core.SliceProxy
jade.core.management.AgentManagementProxy
All Implemented Interfaces:
AgentManagementSlice, Service.Slice, Serializable
public class AgentManagementProxy extends SliceProxy implements AgentManagementSlice
The remote proxy for the JADE kernel-level service managing the basic agent life cycle: creation, destruction, suspension and resumption.
Author:
Giovanni Rimassa - FRAMeTech s.r.l.
